&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Transforming finance and empowering the individual through crypto is a deeply human pursuit. In Business Development you’ll be involved in sales strategy and operations, manage the account lifecycle from prospect to close, and partner with our best-in-industry Customer Success team to build long-lasting relationships with customers that range from innovative startups to leading firms. In addition to CS, you’ll partner closely with marketing, product, and leadership to better understand our target market and grow our pool of addressable AUM.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;The candidate must have 6+ years experience closing business in either the Asset Management, Fintech, or Enterprise SaaS space. Ideally, this person has experience and a passion for building territories from scratch, rather than upselling existing customers.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
