&lt;h4&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Your role in a nutshell:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;As a financial crime investigator, you’ll be involved in preventing and investigating financial crimes like fraud, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;money laundering and account takeovers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; from occurring on Luno. You will report to our Manager Investigations in South Africa. You’ll also be working closely with other Financial Crime team members to help support cross-department operational initiatives to detect and prevent abuse.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You are passionate about cryptocurrencies and their role in the overall fraud and Financial Crime landscape. In your role you will be contributing to setting the standard for Luno’s Financial Crime team in the US.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;The team:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
